OL,3,CBakery and brewery dramatically cuts
OL,4,Cex-prisoner reoffending
OL,6,FThe social enterprise recruits ex-
OL,7,Fprisoners and as ITV Meridian's
OL,8,FNatalie Verney found out, it's
OL,9,Fdramatically reduced reoffending.
OL,11,FA social enterprise in Oxford which
OL,12,Foffers employment to prison leavers
OL,13,Fwants to encourage more businesses to
OL,14,Fdo the same.
OL,16,FThe Tap Social Movement was started in
OL,17,F2016 and now has two brewery's, two
OL,18,Fbars, and a bakery. It's now helped 50
OL,19,Fex-offenders with jobs and just one of
OL,20,Fthem has reoffended.
