OL,6,FThat's in stark contrast to national
OL,7,Fstatistics which show more than half
OL,8,Freoffend in the first year after
OL,9,Frelease.
OL,11,FTwo years ago, life looked very
OL,12,Fdifferent for Terry. He was serving a
OL,13,F15 year prison sentence.
OL,15,FBut now, having served his time, he
OL,16,Fhas a career as a baker at the Proof
OL,17,FSocial Bakehouse.
