OL,3,CBakery and brewery dramatically cuts
OL,4,Cex-prisoner reoffending
OL,6,F"As soon as I got here I loved it. I
OL,7,Floved the bosses here, I loved the
OL,8,Fpeople who work here. They all have
OL,9,Fthe same sort of mentality, they all
OL,10,Fwanted to help and teach and help me
OL,11,Fprogress."
OL,13,FThe company also runs art programmes
OL,14,Finside prisons and all of their
OL,15,Fproducts are covered in prisoner
OL,16,Fartwork.
OL,18,FThey also hold workshops on CVs and
OL,19,Finterview skills to help prepare
OL,20,Finmates as much as possible for their
OL,21,Frelease.
