OL,3,CBakery and brewery dramatically cuts
OL,4,Cex-prisoner reoffending
OL,6,FThe social enterprise has now offered
OL,7,Flong-term employment to 50 prison
OL,8,Fleavers, that's about a third of their
OL,9,Fworkforce and 96 percent of them have
OL,10,Fnot reoffended.
OL,12,F"It's that sense of stability, it's
OL,13,Fthe responsibility, it's being part of
OL,14,Fthe team again it's getting integrated
OL,15,Fwith people and having those normal
OL,16,Fdat-to-day conversations, there's just
OL,17,Fso much that comes with having a job.
OL,18,FAnd it gives people a sense of
OL,19,Fpurpose," said Social Tap co-founder,
OL,20,FTess Taylor.
