OL,3,CBakery and brewery dramatically cuts
OL,4,Cex-prisoner reoffending
OL,6,FTheir results are in stark contrast
OL,7,Fwith national statistics.
OL,9,FA report by the Prison Reform Trust
OL,10,Ffound more than half of prisoners
OL,11,Freoffend within a year of release and
OL,12,Fthe majority of those are unemployed.
OL,14,FThe study also found just a quarter
OL,15,Fare in employment six months after
OL,16,Fleaving prison.
OL,18,FTerry says he found it almost
OL,19,Fimpossible to find work as an ex-
OL,20,Foffender.
