OL,3,CBakery and brewery dramatically cuts
OL,4,Cex-prisoner reoffending
OL,6,F"I was applying for jobs, applying for
OL,7,Fjobs, applying for jobs. Every one of
OL,8,Fthem asked if I had a criminal record
OL,9,Fand as soon as that question was asked
OL,10,Fthe interview went downhill every
OL,11,Ftime," said Terry.
OL,13,F"There's a lot of people that are in
OL,14,Fprison that have some fabulous skill
OL,15,Fthat can do amazing things that have
OL,16,Ftrained in prison to do all sorts from
OL,17,Fcarpentry to cooking to plumbing in
OL,18,Fsome places."
