OL,3,CBakery and brewery dramatically cuts
OL,4,Cex-prisoner reoffending
OL,6,F"We're talking about building more and
OL,7,Fmore prison places but instead what we
OL,8,Fwould really urge and what we are
OL,9,Ftrying to do is shift that
OL,10,Fconversation and look at what support
OL,11,Fcan we be putting in ahead of time so
OL,12,Fthat people aren't ending up in prison
OL,13,Fin the first place."
OL,15,FTess hopes more businesses will be
OL,16,Finspired to help in a similar way.
